\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">\u00bfCu\u00e1l es el horario l\u00edmite para que mi entrega llegue el mismo d\u00eda?<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-9702\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-9702\"><p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><span data-path-to-node=\"4,1\"><span class=\"citation-216\">Debes entregar tus pedidos en nuestra agencia a m\u00e1s tardar a las <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"4,1\" data-index-in-node=\"65\"><span class=\"citation-216\">12:30 pm<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-216\"> para que salgan a ruta ese mismo d\u00eda<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,3\">. <\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,5\"><span class=\"citation-215\">Si los dejas despu\u00e9s de esa hora (hasta las 6:30 pm), tu entrega quedar\u00e1 programada para la tarde del d\u00eda siguiente<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,7\">.<\/span><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-9703\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-9703\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">\u00bfQu\u00e9 beneficios de pago y seguridad incluye este servicio?<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-9703\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-9703\"><p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><span data-path-to-node=\"6,1\"><span class=\"citation-214\">Al igual que nuestros otros servicios, cuentas con un <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"6,1\" data-index-in-node=\"54\"><span class=\"citation-214\">seguro gratuito<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-214\"> que cubre hasta S\/ 300.00 en mercader\u00eda o insumos<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,3\">. <\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,5\"><span class=\"citation-213\">Adem\u00e1s, realizamos el dep\u00f3sito de tus ventas cobradas por contra entrega el mismo d\u00eda, aceptando efectivo, Yape, Plin o tarjeta<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,7\">.<\/span><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4bab13a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4bab13a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1af128 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e1af128\" data-element_typ